<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Myleene Klass has revealed she has got engaged to her boyfriend Simon Motson. </p>

<p>The media personality, 42, admitted she was shocked when her partner popped the question last month on the fifth anniversary of their first date.</p>

<p>Speaking to Hello! magazine, Myleene told how Simon got down on one knee in the couple's garden shed, which he recreated into a replica of the place they had their first date.  </p>

<p>Next step: Myleene Klass, 42, has revealed she has got engaged to her boyfriend Simon Motson</p>

<p>She said: 'We're engaged! I was absolutely blown away. He even replicated the dinner we had – burger and fries, followed by cherry pie.</p>

<p>'When he got down on one knee and started fumbling around under the table, I thought he was joking. Then I thought: "Oh my God, he's for real." I was completely speechless.</p>

<p>Simon added: It's quite a blur but I think I said something along the lines of: 'Myleene Angela Klass, will you marry me?' And I had to say it again... and I think I said it a third time. Finally she said yes and we were both in tears. </p>

<p>The couple's engagement has delighted Myleene's daughters Ava, 13, and Hero, nine, who have been determined to see the couple walk down the aisle. </p>

